========<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34yGdCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34yGdCf.jpg&h=2aced7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gB8C11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gB8C11.jpg&h=f5e08abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aA1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aA1c0.jpg&h=0cd9b552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禮賓府交通路線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n====================<br />\n禮賓府建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n1.急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n2.立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府全部都相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5236ecc6d0cbe6ce811f0a477126f5147f2b56d","tid":1245203,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再問我點解要衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crGMpHH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrGMpHH.jpg&h=4ff620ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n要做的事好簡單 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>6月21 出咗去先</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1245104/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1245104/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7a96f324dbdbf5e7a5b4a66deddf6c3669eface5","tid":1245203,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"So tired no la"},{"pid":"3ad11c3390437a21285fa836dfadd579dce30226","tid":1245203,"uid":245101,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b3efc27d4609411598803be24dc12da5cde4f366","tid":1245203,"uid":60432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:17:28.000Z","msg":"唔出可能有苦衷，而家文革式批鬥？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"下，連登仔不嬲做開文革批鬥"}]}